CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 13, 1952, pg. 27 reads: "Golfdom's Best - Being average wasn't good enough at the South Park golf course last week as the above champions proved in annexing UGA crowns... - Teenie Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of two men, including Gordon Goodson on left, standing at South Park golf course for UGA tournament
